pageProduct.name: Swisse Beauty Collagen Glow Gummies 45 Pack
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Swisse Beauty Collagen Glow Gummies are a delicious beauty nutrition formula, with targeted nutrients to support healthy glowing skin from within. These 99% sugar free gummies are packed full of flavour, contain no artificial sweeteners and are scientifically formulated with potent beauty actives:

Collagen peptides from type I and III collagen - collagen is a major protein found in the dermis of the skin, where the first signs of aging occur.

Vitamin C supports collagen production, skin firmness and elasticity.

Grape seed, vitamin C & E provide antioxidant support to help reduce free radical damage to cells in the body.

Size: 45 Pack

Warnings

Vitamin supplements should not replace a balanced diet. This medicine contains 2.74 g maltitol per maximum daily dose and may have a laxative effect or cause diarrhoea.

Ingredients

EACH GUMMY (PASTILLE) CONTAINS: Hydrolysed Collagen 833.3 mg; Vitamin C (ascorbic acid) 16.67 mg; Vitamin E (dl-alpha-tocopheryl acetate) 2.5 mg; Grape Seed (Vitis vinifera extract 3 mg) equiv. dry seed 360 mg.

Directions

Adult Dosage: Chew 3 gummies daily, during or immediately after a meal, or as directed by a healthcare professional. Do not swallow whole.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C in a cool, dry place away from direct heat.
